{"type":"text","timestamp":1781756291787,"sessionID":"ses_1270ff808ffewqP1i1p6C1RaMp","part":{"id":"prt_ed8f36991001QYACuAs30QvwZO","messageID":"msg_ed8f2f892001FMQijqfaUf493m","sessionID":"ses_1270ff808ffewqP1i1p6C1RaMp","type":"text","text":"The run hit `config.maxIterations: 1`, so synthesis will report `maxIterationsReached` rather than convergence. The lineage verdict is `CONDITIONAL` because the single confirmed finding is P1 and coverage is intentionally incomplete after one pass.","time":{"start":1781756291473,"end":1781756291785},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_014a19d6f38ad4b7016a33718362c08191b00462225841bafb","phase":"commentary"}}}}
